The paper discusses crowdsourced entity resolution and join processing, which are topics related to databases (cs.DB). It also proposes algorithms for solving optimization problems, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem, which is related to theoretical computer science (cs.TC) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) since it involves crowdsourcing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DB, followed by cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SI (since it involves optimization), and cs.HC.
